WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:02.569 --> 00:00:06.072
During a recent search for a missing senior in Nantou, Taiwan...

00:00:06.506 --> 00:00:08.141
I wasn't alone out there.

00:00:11.111 --> 00:00:12.612
WILSON! Is it You?

00:00:14.881 --> 00:00:15.582
Oh.

00:00:15.582 --> 00:00:17.584
It`s just some old helmet!

00:00:20.019 --> 00:00:22.622
The path decides to... move.

00:00:22.989 --> 00:00:25.425
A big snake, just casually crossing the road.

00:00:25.892 --> 00:00:27.427
Near the high voltage poles,

00:00:27.494 --> 00:00:30.764
a huge eagle doing its own inspection of the area.

00:00:31.030 --> 00:00:32.966
then launches into the sky.

00:00:33.333 --> 00:00:34.734
Passing a water reservoir

00:00:34.934 --> 00:00:36.936
carps, just below the surface.

00:00:37.370 --> 00:00:39.105
I asked if they'd seen anything.

00:00:39.339 --> 00:00:40.306
They kept quiet.

00:00:41.107 --> 00:00:42.675
Heavy rain, deep in the forest  

00:00:42.909 --> 00:00:44.644
something is walking on my arm.

00:00:45.045 --> 00:00:46.246
A Joro Spider.

00:00:46.513 --> 00:00:48.481
She was not impressed with me either.

00:00:48.815 --> 00:00:51.418
Crawling on all fours through the bushes  

00:00:51.484 --> 00:00:52.619
suddenly, wild pigs.

00:00:53.086 --> 00:00:55.555
Digging in the soil, preparing their dinner.

00:00:56.956 --> 00:00:57.757
I interrupted.

00:00:58.057 --> 00:00:58.925
They screamed.

00:00:59.092 --> 00:01:00.360
I climbed a tree.

00:01:04.531 --> 00:01:05.465
And then...

00:01:06.032 --> 00:01:08.001
near the forest, in a bamboo farm...

00:01:08.301 --> 00:01:09.602
Something dark.

00:01:09.736 --> 00:01:10.904
Something still.

00:01:11.304 --> 00:01:13.473
Something that should not be disturbed.

00:01:13.740 --> 00:01:14.541
A bear.

00:01:14.941 --> 00:01:15.975
A plush bear.

00:01:16.876 --> 00:01:18.344
Just chilling in the bamboo.

00:01:21.414 --> 00:01:23.483
Taiwan's forests are full of surprises.

00:01:23.817 --> 00:01:25.251
Be safe out there.

00:01:26.186 --> 00:01:26.619
119

00:01:26.619 --> 00:01:27.120
119

00:01:27.120 --> 00:01:27.620
119

00:01:28.488 --> 00:01:29.055
hello!

00:01:29.522 --> 00:01:31.691
Eva: OK! Carefully!

